Global technology leader Cisco is hosting its first-ever Cisco Live all-digital event. Bringing together thousands of customers, employees and other key stakeholders, the event features a two-day conference agenda with sessions facilitated by keynote speakers exploring how Cisco’s technology will drive business outcomes whilst solving current issues in today’s IT accelerated agenda. Cisco will also make several announcements across its networking, security, collaboration, applications, customer experience, and small business portfolios. It said Cisco will continue to seize tomorrow’s digital opportunity today with the objective to share business knowledge, help businesses thrive in the digital age, as a result, create a digital economy. Cisco enjoined participants in the Cisco Live will hold from Tuesday 2nd – Wednesday 3rd June register now for free. 